Reynders Says Belgium to Guarantee 60% of Dexia Bad Bank

-- B y   R e b e c c a   C h r i s t i e
-- 
2011-10-10T01:51:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/reynders-says-belgium-to-guarantee-60-of-dexia-bad-bank.html
Belgian Finance Minister  Didier
Reynders  said  Belgium  will provide a guarantee for 60 percent of
a “bad bank” being set up for  Dexia SA. (DEXB)   He spoke at a press conference today in Brussels.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rebecca Christie in Brussels at 
